/td><td>Repeat purchase</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Read <a href="/alternatives">Shopify alternatives</a>, explore <a href="/use-cases/segmentation">segmentation use cases</a>, or browse <a href="/apps">all Shopify email apps</a>.</p></main></BaseLayout>
